nodes.text: Harrison Deutsch is credited as an assistant voice editor for Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic and Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided and the lead voice editor for Star Wars: Battlefront. He also worked on LEGO Star Wars II: The Original Trilogy, Star Wars: Battlefront II, Star Wars: Republic Commando, Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption, and Star Wars: The Force Unleashed.
